"Sync all complete: %1$d term(s) processed, %2$d translation(s) created, %3$d "
"created as placeholders needing translation, %4$d already up to date, %5$d "
"failed outright — check the AI provider configuration and run it again for "
"those."
msgstr ""
"全部同步完成：已处理 %1$d 个术语，已创建 %2$d 个翻译，%3$d 个作为需要翻译的占"
"位符创建，%4$d 个已是最新，%5$d 个完全失败——请检查 AI 提供商配置后再运行一次"
"处理这些项。"

#. translators: 1: number of primary-language terms processed, 2: number of newly-created translated terms, 3: number of terms created as untranslated placeholders needing a hand edit, 4: number of languages that already had one
#: includes/Admin/TaxonomyLanguageFilter.php:496
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Sync all complete: %1$d term(s) processed, %2$d translation(s) created, %3$d "
"created as untranslated placeholders (AI translation wasn't available for "
"these) — edit them in this list to add the correct name, %4$d already up to "
"date."
msgstr ""
"全部同步完成：已处理 %1$d 个术语，已创建 %2$d 个翻译，%3$d 个作为未翻译占位符"
"创建（这些项不可用 AI 翻译）——请在此列表中编辑它们以添加正确名称，%4$d 个已是"
"最新。"

#. translators: 1: number of primary-language terms processed, 2: number of newly-created translated terms, 3: number of languages that already had one
#: includes/Admin/TaxonomyLanguageFilter.php:505
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Sync all complete: %1$d term(s) processed, %2$d translation(s) created, %3$d "
"already up to date."
msgstr "全部同步完成:已处理 %1$d 个术语,已创建 %2$d 个翻译,%3$d 个已是最新。"

#. translators: 1: number of newly-created translated terms, 2: number of terms created as untranslated placeholders needing a hand edit, 3: number of languages that already had one, 4: number of languages the translation could not be created for at all
#: includes/Admin/TaxonomyLanguageFilter.php:530
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Sync complete: %1$d translation(s) created, %2$d created as placeholders "
"needing translation, %3$d language(s) already up to date, %4$d failed "
"outright — check the AI provider configuration and try again."
msgstr ""
"同步完成：已创建 %1$d 个翻译，%2$d 个作为需要翻译的占位符创建，%3$d 个语言已"
"是最新，%4$d 个完全失败——请检查 AI 提供商配置并重试。"

#. translators: 1: number of newly-created translated terms, 2: number of terms created as untranslated placeholders needing a hand edit, 3: number of languages that already had one
#: includes/Admin/TaxonomyLanguageFilter.php:539
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Sync complete: %1$d translation(s) created, %2$d created as untranslated "
"placeholders (AI translation wasn't available for these) — edit them in this "
"list to add the correct name, %3$d language(s) already up to date."
msgstr ""
"同步完成：已创建 %1$d 个翻译，%2$d 个作为未翻译占位符创建（这些项不可用 AI 翻"
"译）——请在此列表中编辑它们以添加正确名称，%3$d 个语言已是最新。"

#. translators: 1: number of newly-created translated terms, 2: number of languages that already had one
#: includes/Admin/TaxonomyLanguageFilter.php:547
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Sync complete: %1$d translation(s) created, %2$d language(s) already up to "
"date."
msgstr "同步完成:已创建 %1$d 个翻译,%2$d 种语言已是最新。"

#: includes/AI/PromptConfig.php:230
msgid ""
"The artist sent no subject line or message with this submission — let the "
"image speak entirely for itself."
msgstr "这位艺术家在本次提交中没有附上主题或消息——让图片完全自己说话。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:108 includes/Artist/ContactForm.php:145
msgid "Name"
msgstr "名称"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:113
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:514
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:609
msgid "Bio"
msgstr "简介"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:122
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:524
#: includes/Artist/AdmissionNotification.php:619
msgid "Statement"
msgstr "声明"

#. translators: 1: field name (e.g. "Bio", "Message"), 2: maximum character count
#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:178 includes/Artist/ContactForm.php:184
#, php-format
msgid "%1$s must be %2$d characters or fewer."
msgstr "%1$s 的字符数必须少于或等于 %2$d 个。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:228 includes/Artist/JoinPage.php:217
msgid "Please select your language."
msgstr "请选择您的语言。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:237
msgid "An account with this email address already exists."
msgstr "使用此电子邮件地址的账户已存在。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:261
msgid "This email address belongs to an admitted artist."
msgstr "此电子邮件地址属于一位已获录取的艺术家。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:262
msgid "An application for this email address is already pending."
msgstr "此电子邮件地址的申请已在等待审核中。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:609 includes/Artist/Admission.php:717
msgid "Application not found."
msgstr "未找到申请。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:649
msgid "Only admitted artists can vouch."
msgstr "只有已获录取的艺术家才能推荐。"

#: includes/Artist/Admission.php:659
msgid "Admin access required."
