#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:598
msgid ""
"Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept "
"as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it "
"would silently change a settled decision."
msgstr ""
"您写的担保消息已被删除。您投出的治理投票保持原样——投票是一条社区记录，而不是"
"个人数据；删除它会在不知不觉中改变已作出的决定。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:641
msgid ""
"Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts "
"were kept for statistics."
msgstr "过去的新闻邮件投递记录已匿名化；每期的投递数量已保留用于统计。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:708
msgid ""
"Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting "
"point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site's "
"actual configuration before publishing."
msgstr ""
"Agnosis 是一个联邦化艺术发布插件。以下内容是对其收集内容的说明起点——请在发布"
"前根据您网站的实际配置进行审阅并调整。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:709
msgid "What personal data we collect and why"
msgstr "我们收集哪些个人数据，以及为什么收集"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:710
msgid ""
"When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, "
"biography, statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching "
"process. When you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of "
"that email (including your address) is stored while it is processed and "
"reviewed. When you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through "
"their contact form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, "
"your IP address) to deliver that message or send you future issues."
msgstr ""
"当您申请加入时，我们会存储您的电子邮件地址、显示名称、个人简介、陈述和作品集"
"链接，以运行社区担保流程。当您通过电子邮件向我们发送作品、个人简介或活动时，"
"该电子邮件的内容（包括您的地址）会在处理和审核期间被存储。当您订阅我们的新闻"
"邮件或通过艺术家的联系表单向其发送消息时，我们会存储您的电子邮件地址（对于联"
"系消息，还包括您的 IP 地址），以便投递该消息或向您发送未来期刊。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:711
msgid "Who we share it with"
msgstr "我们与谁共享这些数据"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:712
msgid ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."
msgstr ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:721
msgid "Security check (Cloudflare Turnstile)"
msgstr "安全检查（Cloudflare Turnstile）"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:722
msgid ""
"This site uses Cloudflare Turnstile, an automated security check, on its "
"Join, contact, and newsletter-signup forms to block spam submissions. "
"Completing it sends your IP address to Cloudflare for verification."
msgstr ""
"本站在其加入、联系和新闻通讯注册表单上使用 Cloudflare Turnstile（一个自动化安"
"全检查）来阻止垃圾邮件提交。完成它会将您的IP地址发送给Cloudflare进行验证。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:725
msgid "Software updates"
msgstr "软件更新"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:726
msgid ""
"This site checks agnosis.art roughly every 12 hours for available plugin "
"updates. That check includes this site's own web address so the update "
"server can confirm compatibility; no visitor data is involved."
msgstr ""
"本站大约每 12 小时检查一次 agnosis.art 以获取可用的插件更新。该检查包括本站自"
"己的网址，以便更新服务器可以确认兼容性；不涉及访客数据。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:727
msgid "How long we retain your data"
msgstr "我们保留您的数据多久"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:728
msgid ""
"By default: contact-form messages are kept for 90 days, and the sender's IP "
"address on them is cleared sooner, after 30 days. Membership applications "
"that are rejected, withdrawn, or leave the network are anonymized after 180 "
"days. Raw submission emails are deleted from the processing queue after 7 "
"days, and diagnostic copies kept only if this site's administrator has debug "
"logging turned on are deleted after 14 days. This site's administrator can "
"adjust each of these periods under Settings. You can request a copy of, or "
"the erasure of, the personal data described above at any time using this "
"site's standard WordPress data request tools."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下：联系表单消息保留 90 天，发件人的IP地址会更早被清除，在 30 天后。"
"被拒绝、撤回或离开网络的成员资格申请在 180 天后被匿名化。原始投稿电子邮件在处"
"理队列中删除后 7 天，如果本站管理员已打开调试日志记录的诊断副本仅在 14 天后删"
"除。本站管理员可以在设置中调整每个这些时间段。您可以随时使用本站的标准 "
"WordPress 数据请求工具请求复制或擦除上述个人数据。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:756
msgid ""
"Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. "
"Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this "
"cannot be fully undone later."
msgstr ""
"提交的文本和图片可能会由第三方 AI 提供商处理。获批准的帖子会公开发布并在 "
"Fediverse 中共享——这之后无法完全撤销。"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:757
msgid ""
"Your message may be reviewed by an automated content filter before being "
"sent to the artist."
msgstr "您的消息在发送给艺术家之前，可能会先经过自动内容过滤器审核。"

